[thinking] I’m considering the potential issue with having a migration class that's public but not marked final. I think we should avoid using hardcoded artifact versions. It might also be important to note that the native image may not support dynamic class loading. Running tests that load the migration dynamic access by class name at runtime isn't the same as having open-ended dynamic loading after the build, since the class is already present. It's a bit complex, but I’m getting there!
